{"tid":2365691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"眾議員AOC︰(係國會騷亂)  我以為自己會死","createTime":"2021-01-14T03:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T03:33:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c2027e903ddcf554e72a594ea50bf9ac2dfa37c2","tid":2365691,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:20:42.000Z","msg":"民主黨眾議員歐加修&mdash;寇蒂茲（Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez，AOC）在社群媒體上直播描述當日情境，她說，「我不知道自己是否能活下去，那天的情況會讓人極度創傷，這不是在危言聳聽，許多議員可能差點就被刺殺。」<br />\n<br />\nAOC說，她在其他議員身邊感到相當不安，有些同事的行徑恐害她被人傷害、綁架，因為入侵國會者包括極端右翼組織「匿名者Ｑ」及白人至上主義者，而她身邊就有支持白人至上主義的國會議員，可能會暴露她的位置。<br />\n<br />\nAOC提到，她被告知有些全副武裝的暴徒帶著束線帶，似乎是在找尋可當作人質的目標，「身為一名黑人女性，不安全感不是什麼新鮮事，但當日的情況仍相當驚駭。不幸的是，這也和我們過去最深刻的經歷非常相似。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3410467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3410467&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuBPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=cb073feb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3410467&h=f11f802f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3410467</a>"},{"pid":"33203b7d9d8e6df7664e4dd10391390269b5e508","tid":2365691,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"佢係為留歷史紀錄<br />\n將來寫臭侵侵同哩段歷史"},{"pid":"7651a2bfcc9c87e51f812e55be0b96a6953295bb","tid":2365691,"uid":357030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:22:51.000Z","msg":"慳啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723c21a2b2ff8f3f66edb5e532099307d37babb5","tid":2365691,"uid":154373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:23:22.000Z","msg":"Aco d friend <i